To reduce exposure to brute-force attacks, the following controls were proposed:

| Security Control | Purpose |
|---|---|
| Multi-factor authentication | Prevent unauthorized access |
| Password history enforcement | Prevent password reuse |
| Account lockout thresholds | Reduce brute-force attempts |
| Password complexity requirements | Improve credential strength |
| Administrative access restrictions | Reduce privilege abuse |
| Login monitoring and alerting | Improve detection capability |

